================================================================================
In Microsoft's latest 10-K filing, the company discusses its approach and strategy regarding Artificial Intelligence (AI) as follows:

1. **Integration and Growth**:
   - Microsoft is integrating AI into many of its offerings, including productivity services. They are also making AI available for customers to use in their own solutions.
